---
// Final CTA section for Academia Ewaffle
---

<section id="inscripcion" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary via-primary/90 to-primary/80 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background Pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-secondary/20"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Floating Elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-20 h-20 bg-yellow/20 rounded-full blur-xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-accent/20 rounded-full blur-xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/4 w-16 h-16 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-lg"></div>

  <div class="relative container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
        <i class="ri-rocket-line mr-2"></i>
        ¡Únete a la revolución del aprendizaje digital!
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Inscríbete hoy y transforma tu forma de crear contenido educativo
      </h2>
      

      <!-- Benefits Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <i class="ri-download-line text-2xl text-primary"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Materiales Descargables</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm">Plantillas, guías y recursos para usar inmediatamente</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <i class="ri-group-line text-2xl text-white"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Comunidad Exclusiva</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm">Conecta con otros profesionales del sector</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <i class="ri-customer-service-line text-2xl text-white"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Soporte Personalizado</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm">Acompañamiento durante todo tu proceso</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pricing 
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-sm text-white/80 mb-2">Precio especial por tiempo limitado</div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-yellow mb-2">50.000 CLP</div>
          <div class="text-white/80 mb-4">o 50 USD</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-white/60">Cupos limitados - Asegura tu lugar hoy mismo</div>
        </div>
      </div> -->

      <!-- CTA Buttons -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-8">
        <a 
          href="#cursos"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-yellow text-primary rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-yellow/90 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 scroll-smooth scroll-to-section"
        >
          <i class="ri-rocket-line mr-2"></i>
          Inscribirme ahora
        </a>
        
        <a 
          href="https://wa.me/56912345678?text=Hola,%20me%20interesa%20el%20curso%20de%20Academia%20Ewaffle"
          target="_blank"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white/10 text-white border-2 border-white/30 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 scroll-smooth scroll-to-section"
        >
          <i class="ri-whatsapp-line mr-2"></i>
          Consultar por WhatsApp
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Trust Indicators -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow mb-1">500+</div>
          <div class="text-white/80 text-sm">Estudiantes formados</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow mb-1">98%</div>
          <div class="text-white/80 text-sm">Satisfacción</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow mb-1">24/7</div>
          <div class="text-white/80 text-sm">Soporte disponible</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow mb-1">30 días</div>
          <div class="text-white/80 text-sm">Garantía de devolución</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Disclaimer -->
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">
          * Se te redireccionará a la plataforma de pago segura. 
          Acceso inmediato al contenido después del pago.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 